OL,3,CFrank Lampard responds to promotion
OL,4,Cparty hype as Sky Blues rise
OL,6,FFrank Lampard tells ITV News Central
OL,7,Fhe is ignoring growing promotion
OL,8,F"party" talk around Coventry City,
OL,9,Finsisting his focus remains firmly on
OL,10,Fthe job.
OL,12,F"People can talk about parties - I
OL,13,Ffocus on the work," he told ITV News
OL,14,FCentral Sports Correspondent Dan
OL,15,FSalisbury-Jones in Coventry City: The
OL,16,FResurrection, a new documentary now
OL,17,Fstreaming on ITVX charting the Sky
OL,18,FBlues' remarkable rise from crisis to
OL,19,Fcontention.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/10
