OL,3,CFrank Lampard responds to promotion
OL,4,Cparty hype as Sky Blues rise
OL,6,FThe documentary charts the resurgence
OL,7,Fof the Sky Blues, from years of
OL,8,Fturmoil to the brink of a return to
OL,9,Fthe big time, under the leadership of
OL,10,FFrank Lampard.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV News Central, Lampard
OL,13,Falso reflected on his decision to take
OL,14,Fon the role during a difficult period
OL,15,Ffor the club.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
