CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1775931065
OL,3,CFrank Lampard responds to promotion
OL,4,Cparty hype as Sky Blues rise
OL,6,F"No, not necessarily," he said when
OL,7,Fasked if he had imagined his journey
OL,8,Ftaking him to Coventry, before adding:
OL,9,F"But when you take on this line of
OL,10,Fwork, you understand it can take you
OL,11,Fto many different places - the good
OL,12,Fand the bad of it, especially when
OL,13,Fyou've got young children at home."
OL,15,FHe adds: "I thought it was a good
OL,16,Fopportunity to get to work, to come
OL,17,Fand try and impact on the squad at the
OL,18,Ftime when they were having a difficult
OL,19,Ftime."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1775931065
OL,3,CFrank Lampard responds to promotion
OL,4,Cparty hype as Sky Blues rise
OL,6,FHe said the scale of support in
OL,7,FCoventry exceeded expectations.
OL,9,F"I was surprised when I got here in
OL,10,Fterms of the fan base and what we've
OL,11,Fmanaged to get rolling and how it's
OL,12,Fgot to this point. The fan base has
OL,13,Fbeen here long before me and will be
OL,14,Fhere after me - but I wanted to come
OL,15,Fand get to work. Fortunately, we could
OL,16,Fget up and running pretty quickly."
OL,18,FUnder Lampard, performances have
OL,19,Fimproved significantly, with the Sky
OL,20,FBlues emerging as unlikely contenders
OL,21,Fat the top end of the table.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1775931065
OL,3,CFrank Lampard responds to promotion
OL,4,Cparty hype as Sky Blues rise
OL,6,F"Our consistency levels are a vast
OL,7,Fimprovement, so that was amazing. You
OL,8,Fgain confidence in them as you do with
OL,9,Four messaging.
OL,11,F"Were we expected to be in an
OL,12,Fautomatic position at this point?
OL,13,FProbably not - not just from ourselves
OL,14,Fbut from the outside world. The lads
OL,15,Fdeserve a lot of credit. They listen,
OL,16,Fthey train, they stick together -
OL,17,Fthey're the ones that go out on the
OL,18,Fpitch and do it."
OL,20,FDespite the progress, Lampard insists
OL,21,Fthe job is far from finished.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
