PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1775931065
OL,3,CFrank Lampard responds to promotion
OL,4,Cparty hype as Sky Blues rise
OL,6,FHe told ITV: "I'm happy here, I just
OL,7,Fwant to achieve what we want to
OL,8,Fachieve this year, which is not done
OL,9,Fyet."
OL,11,FCoventry City's struggle
OL,13,FThe documentary revisits defining
OL,14,Fmoments in Coventry City's history,
OL,15,Fincluding their famous 1987 FA Cup
OL,16,FFinal triumph under George Curtis and
OL,17,FJohn Sillett.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
