OL,3,CFrank Lampard responds to promotion
OL,4,Cparty hype as Sky Blues rise
OL,6,FIt also explores darker chapters -
OL,7,Ffrom financial crises and
OL,8,Fadministration battles to the club's
OL,9,Fcontroversial ground-sharing spell
OL,10,Faway from the city in 2013 - testing
OL,11,Fthe bond between the team and its
OL,12,Fsupporters.
OL,14,FThe programme highlights the revival
OL,15,Fled by Mark Robins, whose tenure
OL,16,Fdelivered a climb back up the English
OL,17,Ffootball pyramid, as well as the
OL,18,Fstabilising ownership of Doug King and
OL,19,Fthe eventual return to their home
OL,20,Fground.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
