OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1775931065
OL,3,CFrank Lampard responds to promotion
OL,4,Cparty hype as Sky Blues rise
OL,6,FThrough exclusive interviews with
OL,7,Fplayers past and present, club figures
OL,8,Fand supporters, the documentary
OL,9,Fcaptures a community united by its
OL,10,Fteam - including fans Clive and Ash
OL,11,FBrookes, whose shared love of Coventry
OL,12,FCity has helped them navigate personal
OL,13,Fchallenges.
OL,15,FBlending archive footage, on-the-
OL,16,Fstreet interviews and behind-the-
OL,17,Fscenes access, Coventry City: The
OL,18,FResurrection tells a story of
OL,19,Fperseverance and pride - and a club
OL,20,Fonce on the brink now daring to dream
OL,21,Fagain.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
